    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p><em>\"Welcome to Firelink Shrine, Unkindled One. I shall stay by your side until the day you become Cinder.\"</em></p><p><strong>Service — leveling.</strong> Blind, gentle, and bound to the flame, the Fire Keeper turns banked souls into strength. Run the <strong>Level Up</strong> macro and walk the player through the <em>Level-Up Menu Cards</em> journal. She also reinforces the Estus Flask with Estus Shards (add a charge, cap 6). Non-combatant — if she is ever threatened, the scene is already lost.</p>",
